		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I connected my famicom to my PC using my old PCI tv-tuner card. Successful, more or less. The image quality was very bad. The audio was, hm. well, nothing, just noise sadly.
<br />My tv-tuner card works with NTSC so that's not the problem ( I think).
<br />I'm thinking of getting a newer tv-tuner card and perhaps the problems will be gone(?). Anyone have any hints on what I should get? Are there any special features that is required to get it to work properly with the famicom?
<br />
