	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Even the worst cards should be able to capture the image with decent quality.
<br />
<br />Do other things work well with the card (tv channels or a VCR, maybe)? Do you have sound with the other stuff?
<br />
<br />Are you using RF? Don't you need to connect the sound from the tuner card into the sound card (line in) to get any sound in this case? It had to be done like this on my old ATI card. Maybe that's why you don't have sound?

		

